</kw><br>
<br><kw class="krdwrd-tag-3">
2) Don't know
</kw><br>
<br><kw class="krdwrd-tag-3">
3) No, because the crew is allowed to vote for a new captain in most ships (it depends really), but if the crew were to forcefully make some one else captain, and threaten or actually hurt the captain then that would be a mutiny.
</kw><br>
<br><kw class="krdwrd-tag-3">
4) Don't know again, sorry
