<div class="PhorumReadBodySubject"><kw class="krdwrd-tag-2">Re: Ship ownership</kw></div>
<div class="PhorumReadBodyHead"><kw class="krdwrd-tag-1">Posted by: </kw><strong><a href="http://www.piratesinfo.com/mysql/phorum/profile.php?1,1696"><kw class="krdwrd-tag-1">Aaron Whifflingpin</kw></a></strong><kw class="krdwrd-tag-1"> (---.glfd.dial.virgin.net)</kw></div>
