<a name="msg-14218"></a>
<div class="PhorumReadMessageBlock">
<div class="PhorumStdBlock">
<div class="PhorumReadBodySubject"><kw class="krdwrd-tag-1">Re: Ship ownership</kw></div>
<div class="PhorumReadBodyHead"><kw class="krdwrd-tag-1">Posted by: </kw><strong><a href="http://www.piratesinfo.com/mysql/phorum/profile.php?1,194"><kw class="krdwrd-tag-1">daniel</kw></a></strong><kw class="krdwrd-tag-1"> (209.106.200.---)</kw></div>
<div class="PhorumReadBodyHead"><kw class="krdwrd-tag-1">Date: 29 November 2004, 09:32PM</kw></div>
<br>
<div class="PhorumReadBodyText"><kw class="krdwrd-tag-3"> I do not have the exact quote here, just my own note saying that "The men estimated Russel/Lopez's sway with the crew at twice Low's."
</kw><br>
<br><kw class="krdwrd-tag-3">
My notes do contain this direct quote, however: "That if any of the Company shall advise, or speak any thing tending to the separating or breaking of the Company, or shall by any means offer or endeavour to desert or quit the Company, that Person shall be shot to Death by the Quarter-Master's Order, without the Sentence of a Court-Martial."  This to me implies a degree of authority exerted independent of the crew, unless the crew replaces him.
</kw><br>
<br><kw class="krdwrd-tag-3">
The book is "The Four Years Voyages of Cap. George Roberts" dated 1726.</kw></div><br>
</div>


<div class="PhorumReadNavBlock" style="text-align: left;">
<span class="PhorumNavHeading PhorumHeadingLeft"><kw class="krdwrd-tag-1">Options:</kw></span>&nbsp;<a class="PhorumNavLink" href="http://www.piratesinfo.com/mysql/phorum/read.php?1,13739,14218#REPLY"><kw class="krdwrd-tag-1">Reply To This Message</kw></a><kw class="krdwrd-tag-1">•</kw><a class="PhorumNavLink" href="http://www.piratesinfo.com/mysql/phorum/read.php?1,13739,14218,quote=1#REPLY"><kw class="krdwrd-tag-1">Quote This Message</kw></a><kw class="krdwrd-tag-1">•</kw><a class="PhorumNavLink" href="javascript:if(window.confirm('Are you sure you want to report this post?')) window.location='http://www.piratesinfo.com/mysql/phorum/read.php?1,13739,14218,report=1#msg-14218';"><kw class="krdwrd-tag-1">Report This Message</kw></a></div>

